 Trackers integrate with AI features?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Tracker data in the EHR provides context for AI Scribe, helping providers generate richer, more accurate consultation notes.\"},{\"question\":\"Can clinics customize which trackers are available?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. Admins choose which subset of the 70+ trackers is relevant for their practice or individual patients.\"},{\"question\":\"Is tracker data secure and compliant?\",\"answer\":\"Yes. All data is stored securely within the EHR and managed under strict healthcare privacy and security standards.\"}],\"final_cta\":{\"title\":\"Ready to Put Health Trackers Into Practice?\",\"subtitle\":\"Monitor 70+ health parameters directly in the EHR — with device sync, patient collaboration, and Remote Patient Monitoring built in.\",\"button_text\":\"Start Free Trial\",\"description\":\"Experience how data flows from patients, providers, and devices into the record — powering continuous care without disrupting your workflows.\"},\"cta_section\":{\"title\":\"Ready to Enhance Patient Care with Health Tracking?\",\"subtitle\":\"Improve patient outcomes and engagement with comprehensive health tracking that integrates seamlessly with your practice management system.\",\"description_title\":\"Advanced health tracking included in all plans\",\"description_text\":\"Multi-device integration, real-time monitoring, goal tracking, provider alerts, and comprehensive analytics - everything you need for proactive patient care.\"}},\"health_blog_platform\":{\"meta\":{\"title\":\"Health Blog Platform for Clinics | ContinuousCare Patient Engagement\",\"description\":\"Build trust and improve outcomes by sharing professional, practice-created health tips and articles that educate and connect with your patient community.\"},\"hero\":{\"title\":\"Engage Patients with Your Health Blog\",\"title_highlight\":\"Health Blog\",\"subtitle\":\"Build trust and improve outcomes by sharing professional, practice-created health tips and articles that